OL,3,CUK defence 'spending gap' is 'matter
OL,4,Cof concern for Nato', says former chief
OL,6,FA UK "spending gap" on defence would
OL,7,Fbe "a matter of concern for Nato", a
OL,8,Fformer secretary-general of the
OL,9,Falliance has said.
OL,11,FAnders Fogh Rasmussen's warning came
OL,12,Famid a row over defence spending that
OL,13,Fsaw John Healey quit as defence
OL,14,Fsecretary.
OL,16,FMr Healey resigned on June 11, citing
OL,17,Fa lack of funding for the long-delayed
OL,18,FDefence Investment Plan (Dip) and
OL,19,Farguing there was "no path" to
OL,20,Freaching the Nato target of spending
OL,21,F3.5% of GDP on core defence by 2035.
OL,26,@nD@FOUnD@SO]oD@DOUoD@aO]{D@SOU{D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
