PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782299900
OL,3,CUK defence 'spending gap' is 'matter
OL,4,Cof concern for Nato', says former chief
OL,6,FSpeaking to the Press Association on a
OL,7,Fvisit to London, Mr Rasmussen declined
OL,8,Fto comment on the UK's internal
OL,9,Fpolitics, but said: "A spending gap in
OL,10,Fthe UK is a matter of concern for the
OL,11,Frest of Nato.
OL,13,F"We have seen how the Spanish Prime
OL,14,FMinister (Pedro) Sanchez has raised
OL,15,Fdoubts of his commitments to the
OL,16,Fdecision made at the Nato summit in
OL,17,FThe Hague and if there are doubts
OL,18,Fabout the UK trajectory towards that
OL,19,Fgoal, it is a matter of concern in
OL,20,Fother countries."
OL,26,@qD@UOUuD@AOU|D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
