CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782299900
OL,3,CUK defence 'spending gap' is 'matter
OL,4,Cof concern for Nato', says former chief
OL,6,FBut he added the UK was "a reliable
OL,7,Fpartner when it comes to defence and
OL,8,Fsecurity" that was still "playing an
OL,9,Fimportant role" in Nato.
OL,11,FMinisters have repeatedly said the Dip
OL,12,Fwill be published before the Nato
OL,13,Fsummit that begins in Ankara on July 7
OL,14,Fand the Government remains committed
OL,15,Fto meeting the alliance's spending
OL,16,Ftarget.
OL,26,@nD@YOUpD@IO]pD@ZOUqD@OO]
