OL,3,CUK defence 'spending gap' is 'matter
OL,4,Cof concern for Nato', says former chief
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, Mr Healey's successor, Dan
OL,7,FJarvis, told a defence conference in
OL,8,FLondon he had already assured current
OL,9,FNato secretary-general Mark Rutte that
OL,10,Fthe target would be met "and a
OL,11,Fcredible plan will be produced to
OL,12,Fensure that it is".
OL,14,FBut he conceded that he had "a job of
OL,15,Fwork to do to map out that trajectory"
OL,16,Fto 3.5% by 2035.
OL,26,@rD@YOUtD@RO]vD@]OUwD@fO]
