FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782299900
OL,3,CUK defence 'spending gap' is 'matter
OL,4,Cof concern for Nato', says former chief
OL,6,FThe target includes an agreement to
OL,7,Fspend 3.5% of GDP on "core defence"
OL,8,Fand another 1.5% on measures to boost
OL,9,Fnational resilience by 2035.
OL,11,FMr Rasmussen said he expected next
OL,12,Fmonth's Nato summit in Ankara to see
OL,13,Fallies asked to present "a clear plan
OL,14,Fand a timeline" for reaching the 5%
OL,15,Ftarget.
OL,17,FBut pointing to warnings Russia could
OL,18,Fbe ready to attack Nato as early as
OL,19,F2030, he told PA the 2035 target was
OL,20,F"too weak" and "should be much faster".
OL,26,@oD@VOUoD@cO]uD@YOUvD@OO]|D@AOU|D@JO]|D@
OL,26,APOU|D@fO]
