PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782299900
OL,3,CUK defence 'spending gap' is 'matter
OL,4,Cof concern for Nato', says former chief
OL,6,FHe said Nato should look to spend at
OL,7,Fleast 3.5% of GDP on core defence by
OL,8,F2030, adding: "As an example, the new
OL,9,FDanish government has decided to reach
OL,10,F3.5% by 2030, so it is realistic and a
OL,11,Fnumber of Baltic states have done the
OL,12,Fsame."
OL,14,FAs a former Danish prime minister, he
OL,15,Fsaid he understood that this was "a
OL,16,Fchallenge for all governments" who
OL,17,Ffaced either cutting spending or
OL,18,Fraising taxes to meet the target.
OL,26,@pD@OOUtD@FO]wD@bOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782299900
OL,3,CUK defence 'spending gap' is 'matter
OL,4,Cof concern for Nato', says former chief
OL,6,FBut he added: "I understand very well
OL,7,Fthat many ministers of finance would
OL,8,Fsay, if you are broke, you're not safe.
OL,10,F"That's true, I understand that very
OL,11,Fwell, but my whole point is if you
OL,12,Fdon't invest sufficiently in defence,
OL,13,Fif you don't spend enough, if you
OL,14,Fdon't do it fast enough and if you
OL,15,Fdon't spend the money on the right
OL,16,Fthings, then you are not safe.
OL,18,F"So you have to find the right
OL,19,Fbalance, and I think this will be the
OL,20,Ffocal point in Ankara."
OL,26,@nD@OOUrD@AOUzD@AOU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
