CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782299900
OL,3,CUK defence 'spending gap' is 'matter
OL,4,Cof concern for Nato', says former chief
OL,6,FMr Rasmussen also called for a
OL,7,Fdiscussion at the Ankara summit of
OL,8,Fwhat areas defence spending should
OL,9,Ffocus on, saying: "We're not spending
OL,10,Fon the right stuff."
OL,12,FHe said: "Where to invest will be put
OL,13,Fin a much stronger focus now.
OL,15,F"We have seen how Ukraine has been
OL,16,Fable to develop new military
OL,17,Fcapabilities, drones and other high-
OL,18,Ftech military capabilities, that are
OL,19,Fvery efficient.
OL,26,@qD@SOUrD@TO]tD@JOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
