OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782299900
OL,3,CUK defence 'spending gap' is 'matter
OL,4,Cof concern for Nato', says former chief
OL,6,F"They are less expensive than what I
OL,7,Fwould call the legacy military
OL,8,Fcapabilities. They can be produced
OL,9,Fmuch, much faster, and actually, they
OL,10,Fhave demonstrated high efficiency.
OL,12,F"Today, more people are killed by
OL,13,Fdrones than by artillery in Ukraine."
OL,15,FAs with last year's Nato summit, the
OL,16,Fmeeting in Ankara will be overshadowed
OL,17,Fby doubts about the USA's commitment
OL,18,Fto the alliance.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUuD@eO]
