OL,3,CUK defence 'spending gap' is 'matter
OL,4,Cof concern for Nato', says former chief
OL,6,FSince the start of the year, Mr Trump
OL,7,Fhas threatened to annex Greenland,
OL,8,Fwhich belongs to Nato ally Denmark,
OL,9,Fand has criticised allies for their
OL,10,Frefusal to provide military support
OL,11,Ffor his attack on Iran.
OL,13,FLast week, US defence secretary Pete
OL,14,FHegseth announced a review of American
OL,15,Fmilitary forces in Europe at a meeting
OL,16,Fof Nato defence ministers, criticising
OL,17,Fmembers who "have yet to show a
OL,18,Fcredible path" towards meeting their
OL,19,Fspending commitments.
OL,26,@yD@MOUzD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
