SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782299900
OL,3,CUK defence 'spending gap' is 'matter
OL,4,Cof concern for Nato', says former chief
OL,6,FBut Mr Rasmussen, who was outspoken in
OL,7,Fhis criticism of the US over Mr
OL,8,FTrump's threats to take Greenland,
OL,9,Fsaid he was optimistic about the
OL,10,Ffuture of the alliance and confident
OL,11,Fthat issues with the US would be
OL,12,Fresolved.
OL,14,FWhile acknowledging that the alliance
OL,15,Fwas "challenged", he said statements
OL,16,Fat this month's G7 summit had been
OL,17,F"encouraging".
OL,26,@wD@EOUwD@PO]yD@AOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
