OL,3,CUK defence 'spending gap' is 'matter
OL,4,Cof concern for Nato', says former chief
OL,6,FHe told PA: "You have seen joint
OL,7,Fstatements on Ukraine and continued
OL,8,FAmerican commitment, while at the same
OL,9,Ftime we realise in Europe that we have
OL,10,Fto do more.
OL,12,F"I think President Trump has realised
OL,13,Fthe connection between Iran and
OL,14,FRussia. He knows very well that the
OL,15,Fconflicts may be interlinked, and as
OL,16,Fhe is struggling with Iran, Russia has
OL,17,Factually supported and is supporting
OL,18,FIran.
OL,20,F"So I think that has also sharpened
OL,21,Fthe view of President Trump."
OL,26,@nD@MOUtD@AOU|D@AOU}D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
