OL,3,CUK defence 'spending gap' is 'matter
OL,4,Cof concern for Nato', says former chief
OL,6,FBut he also suggested a new "coalition
OL,7,Fof the willing" within Nato, led by
OL,8,FBritain and France that included
OL,9,FEuropean nations and Ukraine,
OL,10,Fproviding a "strong European-led
OL,11,Fnuclear deterrence in addition to the
OL,12,Foverall American nuclear umbrella".
